      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Amazon.com's new cooking destination (Amazon.comkitchen) is a full-service Web site, offering cookware and housewares, equipment evaluations by writers at Cook's Illustrated, plus recipes and tips from cookbook authors.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>Amazon.com's new cooking destination (Amazon.comkitchen) is a full-service Web site, offering cookware and housewares, equipment evaluations by writers at Cook's Illustrated, plus recipes and tips from cookbook authors.</p>
        <p>Though the site may offer good advice on, say, how to choose a knife, there's no substitute for picking one up in a store and getting the feel of it. Amazon.com's prices also aren't the lowest available, so you may want to do some comparison shopping.</p>
        <p>FOOD STUFF The Food Stuff column now appears every other week, alternating with the Eating Well column.</p>
      </block>
